{"tid":2035374,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"「遊行主題」點解冇人搞遊行要求調查漢武肺炎源頭？","createTime":"2020-05-26T00:54:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T01:17:19.000Z","uid":2438,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"626ae3dddf09f4e7288fa8dd56eb74b96bc4797a","tid":2035374,"uid":2438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T00:54:33.000Z","msg":"小弟想提議下，遊行嘅主題可以同國際接軌。<br />\n<br />\n打國際戰線就要將遊行嘅主題提升到國際嘅議題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有「感謝全球醫護」、「哀悼全球武肺死者」、「全球立即制裁中國」等等<br />\n<br />\n中共想回避嘅話題，我哋就日日講。通過國際新聞，我哋可以令外國人覺得香港同佢哋同一陣線，爭取民意。可能的話，外國民眾會向政府施壓，要求政府正視香港問題。人哋民主社會，政府需要聽取民意的。"},{"pid":"15b71306ac22b015d79fde0d68b3e575bb4ae13c","tid":2035374,"uid":177089,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T01:00:34.000Z","msg":"因為我地主線好撚多"},{"pid":"1955af080a2a4752521fa297700317bdb7ea1d04","tid":2035374,"uid":145273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T01:04:59.000Z","msg":"國安法一過，你覺得武漢肺炎依4隻字仲可以出到街？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b192c138492932872414438dac43b827a81e9a65","tid":2035374,"uid":2438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15b71306ac22b015d79fde0d68b3e575bb4ae13c","tid":2035374,"uid":177089,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T01:00:34.000Z","msg":"因為我地主線好撚多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T01:06:29.000Z","msg":"我意思係，忙完主線，都可以打下國際線嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果返返去武肺之前，每星期都有遊行，咁咪可以考慮用下國際主題connect外國議題"},{"pid":"1b1cc0a629262b760637f42510e4db454802e875","tid":2035374,"uid":2438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1955af080a2a4752521fa297700317bdb7ea1d